trans-unit.source: Represents objects that support synchronized input events.
trans-unit.target: Representerer objekter som støtter synkroniserte inndata hendelser.

trans-unit.source: Stops listening for input.
trans-unit.target: Stopper lytting på inndata.

trans-unit.source: If the provider is currently listening for input, it reverts to normal operation.
trans-unit.target: Hvis leverandøren lytter på inndata, går tilbake til vanlig drift.

trans-unit.source: Identifies the event raised when WPF discards input.
trans-unit.target: Identifiserer hendelsen som opprettes når WPF ignorerer inndata.

trans-unit.source: This identifier is used by UI Automation client applications.
trans-unit.target: Denne identifikatoren brukes av Brukergrensesnittet Automation klientprogrammer.

trans-unit.source: A UI Automation provider should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPatternIdentifiers>.
trans-unit.target: Leverandør Brukergrensesnittet automatisering må bruke det tilsvarende feltet i <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPatternIdentifiers>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPatternIdentifiers>

trans-unit.source: Identifies the <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPattern"></xref> control pattern.
trans-unit.target: Identifiserer den <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPattern"> </xref> kontrollen mønsteret.

trans-unit.source: This identifier is used by UI Automation client applications.
trans-unit.target: Denne identifikatoren brukes av Brukergrensesnittet Automation klientprogrammer.

trans-unit.source: UI Automation providers should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPatternIdentifiers>.
trans-unit.target: Brukergrensesnittet Automation leverandører må bruke det tilsvarende feltet i <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPatternIdentifiers>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPatternIdentifiers>

trans-unit.source: The pattern identifier is passed to methods, such as <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPattern%2A>, to retrieve the control pattern of interest from the specified <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>.
trans-unit.target: Mønsteret-identifikatoren som er sendt til metoder, for eksempel <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPattern%2A>å hente kontrollen mønsteret interessante fra den angitte <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPattern%2A>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Designates that the provider start listening for input of the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Angir som leverandøren starten lytter for å registrere den angitte typen.

trans-unit.source: When WPF finds matching input, it checks the route of the incoming event.
trans-unit.target: Når WPF finner samsvarende inndata, kontrollerer ruten for den innkommende hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: If the automation element that is listening for the input is not in the route, the input is discarded and the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPattern.InputDiscardedEvent> event is raised.
trans-unit.target: Hvis elementet automation lytter for inndataene ikke er i ruten, forkastes inndataene og <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPattern.InputDiscardedEvent>denne hendelsen oppstår.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPattern.InputDiscardedEvent>

trans-unit.source: If the input is received by the automation element listening for that type, the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPattern.InputReachedTargetEvent> event is raised; otherwise, the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPattern.InputReachedOtherElementEvent> event is raised.
trans-unit.target: Hvis de er mottatt av elementet automation lytter for denne typen i <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPattern.InputReachedTargetEvent>hendelsen er hevet; motsatt fall, av <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPattern.InputReachedOtherElementEvent>denne hendelsen oppstår.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPattern.InputReachedOtherElementEvent> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.SynchronizedInputPattern.InputReachedTargetEvent>

trans-unit.source: After receiving the input, the provider stops listening and continues normally.
trans-unit.target: Leverandøren stopper lytte etter mottak av inndataene, og fortsetter normalt.

trans-unit.source: The type of input to listen for.
trans-unit.target: Inngangstypen å lytte etter.
